{"tid":667993,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門返緊工嘅你好call定直升機","createTime":"2018-05-17T08:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T09:10:28.000Z","uid":38041,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5328fcf040da75102a4a0cf079b9e265451790cb","tid":667993,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:21:38.000Z","msg":"深井屯門公路向屯門方向，下午3時20分發生交通意外。據報現場多部車輛相撞，當中涉及一部旅遊巴與一輛貨車，初步最少15人受傷。大批救援人員正在現場拯救。<br />\n<br />\n受交通意外影響，屯門公路往屯門方向近浪翠園的部份行車線仍然封閉，駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車。現時在屯門公路往屯門方向的車龍龍尾至4公里外的汀九橋。"},{"pid":"726697b6a304ec1cf8b6ad7fbb7963a65782acab","tid":667993,"uid":101193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:24:45.000Z","msg":"一入你個post就塞車"},{"pid":"12e68f260a371179a15e3868b3443ef9c2d6e7a4","tid":667993,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4327cadba9cd40abdc9d561bbfd93be1cf60f634","tid":667993,"uid":98507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:50:24.000Z","msg":"屯門出九龍冇野 入屯門先出事姐"},{"pid":"f0aab7438adc30b0f3c5ecb32f84c80b8588f589","tid":667993,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"今晚約左人食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1104763d0929dea4738d54f218b7e0044a54f13","tid":667993,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4327cadba9cd40abdc9d561bbfd93be1cf60f634","tid":667993,"uid":98507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:50:24.000Z","msg":"屯門出九龍冇野 入屯門先出事姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:56:42.000Z","msg":"無巴士入會唔會無車出?"},{"pid":"67b1e9ca2bc97e087d90733abcb32e8dc598d192","tid":667993,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3596cac208695353b7321c8cdcded6c3d358f57a","tid":667993,"uid":17747,"like":0,"dislike":0,